{"tid":679165,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"星火同盟　5月27日下午5時至7時　金鐘夏慤道連儂牆　集會聲援義士　vs　支聯會六四遊行","createTime":"2018-05-26T15:45:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T03:49:03.000Z","uid":47714,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"49bab0fc1b42a0138c86a9141eec4c33d5f1d212","tid":679165,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T15:45:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/posts/2176447112642409/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsparkalliancehk%2Fposts%2F2176447112642409%2F&d=%2FFDl4tNWdydqFIjJ58siVxxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=07e32641\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/posts/2176447112642409/</a><br />\n<br />\n【義士陷黑獄，星火送暖光】<br />\n<br />\n自雨傘革命後，港共政權日漸變本加厲，無數市民奮起反抗暴政，終致2016年的魚蛋革命，捍衛港人的生存空間。<br />\n<br />\n魚革後，港共政權羅織暴動罪名，將暴動罪名套在無辜市民身上。由二九年華的青年，到年輕有為的大學生，甚至年近古稀的老人，紛紛被打入冤獄，在長達數年的審訊中，失去了無價的自由與數以年計的光陰，更飽受肉體與精神上的折磨。<br />\n<br />\n這些熱心的市民，為了捍衛港人的自由，無私奉獻，挺身而出。今日，他們犧牲了自己的青春與未來，成為了港共暴政之下又一群的政治犯，自此與家人天各一方。值此危難關頭，他們需要每一個有血性的香港人出手相助。<br />\n<br />\n對於這些捨身就義的義人們，星火同盟抗爭支援一直為他們提供支持與幫助。在五月二十七日下午五時至晚上七時，我們將舉辦聲援義士集會，在義士們身陷囹圄的艱苦時刻，希望香港人能站出來，為他們送上支持與祝福，讓他們不致孤軍奮戰。每一位出席的香港人，都是支持他們撐下去的精神支柱，我們呼籲所有有良知的市民，到場支持他們。我們要讓義士看到，香港人並沒有遺忘他們的貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n集會現場將設立攤位，以提供心意卡讓市民親手書寫，希望大家踴躍參與，為在囚義士及他們家人送上鼓勵與祝福。<br />\n<br />\n日期: 2018年5月27日 (星期日)<br />\n時間: 下午5時至晚上7時<br />\n地點: 金鐘夏慤道連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林微塵:<br />\n那天大遊行好多人會在那地方最後集合<br />\n同埋星火團體已經申請了有不反對通知書！<br />\n大致上是安全的<br />\n<br />\nNick Wong:<br />\n同時間有六四遊行往中聯辦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/438696663227645/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F438696663227645%2F&d=%2FFDl4tNWdydqFIjJ58siVxxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=3e650976\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/438696663227645/</a><br />\n<br />\n支聯會「六四」29周年悼念活動 <br />\n&quot;June 4&quot; 29th Anniversary Memorial Events<br />\n<br />\n日期：2018年5月27日（星期日）2018<br />\n時間：下午３時集合<br />\n地點：灣仔修頓球場至西區中聯辦"},{"pid":"24db509790dca0c5e2b956e85be5737cf2fa1e7c","tid":679165,"uid":47714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T15:47:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://goo.gl/naagLG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FnaagLG&h=9d37f6a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2920f51f0b2970498327fe8e43225d28d629672","tid":679165,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T15:47:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba1f54de4b365b4476a32b9dea72ad306424ddc7","tid":679165,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T03:14:18.000Z","msg":"冇人推既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9fb66c6dcfab05c3a7423a561959b3b8c30a7eb","tid":679165,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T03:17:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a436ebbf1b9e7e3a6827b0c64448de649b0a965","tid":679165,"uid":33642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T03:34:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d52512798d3f6a9432023a8f0a228157dd749ab3","tid":679165,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T03:35:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5339db6732016729aeacd925dec2ae59cf8813","tid":679165,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T03:36:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6fdc2051accccce5300d5404231eabc15f5f5959","tid":679165,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T03:38:36.000Z","msg":"兩日連住，衰鳩硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b72b74e91c0f0a84bddc643365794e46860f95","tid":679165,"uid":99364,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy